WEBVTT

00:13:57.960 --> 00:14:01.072
but they are powerless
to bring any change.

00:14:01.072 --> 00:14:03.579
They have to learn to accept it

00:14:03.579 --> 00:14:06.958
and gradually turn this
into positive energy.

00:14:06.958 --> 00:14:08.407
It's difficult.

00:14:08.407 --> 00:14:10.945
Many don't succeed,

00:14:10.945 --> 00:14:14.953
but for those who do,
there is no other job like this.

00:14:14.953 --> 00:14:18.733
You can see the difference
you make every day.

00:14:19.643 --> 00:14:22.805
Humanitarian aid workers
know the risk they are taking

00:14:22.805 --> 00:14:27.717
in conflict areas or 
in post-conflict environments,

00:14:27.717 --> 00:14:34.429
yet our life, our job, is becoming 
increasingly life-threatening,